creator: George MacDonald
description:
LibriVox recording of The Wind and the Moon by George MacDonald.

Read in English by Bryony Ford; Claudia Salto; David Lawrence; Eric Metzler; Ezwa; Jason Mills; Julia Niedermaier; Jothi Tharavant; Leonard Wilson; MaryAnn Spiegel; Marina Tsung; Rosslyn Carlyle; Sweet Pea; and Shakira Searle.

Librivox volunteers bring you 15 readings of The Wind and the Moon by George Macdonald. This is the fortnightly poetry project for September 28, 2014.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (22MB)
